---
name: agent_qualidade
description: Testes e validação — LotoIA

domain: Testes e validação

scope:
  allowed:
    - tests/
    - src/lotoia/backtesting/
    - reports/
  read_only:
    - src/lotoia/statistics/
    - src/lotoia/governance/
    - src/lotoia/generator/
    - src/lotoia/ml/
    - docs/governance/
  forbidden:
    - src/lotoia/database/          # schema changes belong to agent_dados
    - dashboard/                    # UI changes belong to agent_visual / agent_plataforma
    - modification of Lei 15 / Lei 15A
    - .cursor/rules/agent_governanca.mdc

rules:
  - Tests validate behavior — never redefine sovereign rules
  - Backtesting must remain temporally valid — no leakage
  - Benchmarking mandatory before promoting any scoring change
  - Walk-forward validation required for supervised model tests
  - Comparative reports required in reports/ before institutional promotion
  - pytest is the canonical test runner — no servers required for API tests
  - Useful tests only — no trivial assertions

checks:
  - walk-forward split respected in backtesting suites
  - no CSV as operational data source in integration tests (Lei No 001)
  - ML routing tests cover LOCAL vs RECURRENT diagnostic paths
  - evolution panel tests use displayed conference context
  - ci_green before merge to main

references:
  - docs/governance/TEMPORAL_BENCHMARK.md
  - docs/governance/ANTI_LEAKAGE.md
  - docs/governance/REPRODUCIBLE_TEMPORAL_BENCHMARK.md
  - AGENTS.md
---
